# Schola Job Guide — Actuary (Aktuari)

Bilingual (EN/BM) job guide for the Actuary career on Schola.org.my. Used as a knowledge source by [[entities/Ola]].

**Schola URL (EN):** https://schola.org.my/en/jobs/actuary  
**Schola URL (BM):** https://schola.org.my/ms/pekerjaan/aktuari

## Overview

- **Industry:** Banking & Finance
- **Aliases:** Valuation Actuary, Actuarial Executive, Mathematician, Demographer
- **Definition:** Uses maths and statistics to help companies predict financial risks, unexpected events, and future expenses.
- **High income potential:** Yes; degree required for entry

## Salary & Career Progression

| Career Level | Salary Range (RM) | Typical Titles | Years Experience |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Early Career | 2,800–7,000 | Associate / Sekutu | 0 |
| Supervisory | 3,500–9,000 | Senior Associate / Sekutu Kanan | ~2 |
| Managerial | 8,000–19,000 | Manager / Pengurus | ~6 |
| Leadership | 30,000–75,000+ | Appointed Actuary / Aktuari Dilantik | ~15 |

Salary increases with each actuarial exam passed (potentially adding up to RM7,000 per exam). Sources: Jobstreet, Mudah.my, MYFutureJobs, Maukerja, Hays Salary Guide 2024, Glassdoor (all accessed 2024).

## Education Pathways

Two routes:

| Stage | Degree Pathway (4–6 yrs) | Professional Certification Pathway (7–13 yrs) |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Pre-U | STPM / Asasi / Matriks / A-Levels / Foundation | Same |
| Degree | Actuarial Science (3–4 yrs) | Any degree (3–4 yrs) |
| Certification | — | Actuarial Exams: IFoA or SOA (3–7 yrs) |
| Entry title | Actuarial Associate | Certified Actuary |

Actuarial Science graduates may receive exam exemptions. A non-Actuarial Science degree is viable but professional exams are mandatory for certification.

## Expert Insights

**[[entities/Farhana]] (Actuary):**
- Heavy use of Excel and some coding; applies maths, statistics, and financial theory to predict risks
- Start in entry-level roles, then pass IFoA/SOA professional exams over 3–7 years while working
- Actuaries can become non-Actuarial Science graduates if they pass the professional exams
- In high demand in insurance companies and consulting firms, globally after certification

**[[entities/Anisha-Puri]] (Actuary, Allianz Malaysia):**
- Certification allows appointment as an Appointed Actuary with authority over financial decisions and regulatory approvals
- Salary increases substantially with each exam passed

## Demand

- High demand in insurance companies and consulting firms
- Global opportunities after gaining experience and certification
- Skills transferable to fintech and business analytics

